---
title: Roasted Mushroom Risotto with Goat Cheese
description: This weeknight-ready risotto takes less time but it’s just as satisfying! Roasting the mushrooms brings out deep mushroom flavour and stirring in goat cheese adds a zippy creaminess. We've also added green peas for bites of freshness and toasted almonds for crunch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/risotto-aux-champignons-rotis-c0bd54d0.jpg
